!config/*.csv
# Frozen canonical ASRI series = the paper's dataset of record (max 84.70,
# sha256 in DATA_PROVENANCE.md; Zenodo 10.5281/zenodo.17918239). Ship it in-repo
# so the analysis scripts reproduce every headline on a fresh clone. All OTHER
# *.parquet (regens, pegfix sensitivities, smoke outputs) stay ignored.
!results/data/asri_history.parquet
# Live-dashboard continuation series: the exact rows loaded into D1 for
# 2026-01-16.., plus the append-only audit log of every later live refresh
# (see RUNBOOK_DASHBOARD.md).
!results/data/asri_backfill_2026H1.parquet
!results/data/asri_live_appends.csv
# Real peg-history input (drives the Bug-3 peg-fix sensitivity).
!data/peg_history.csv
# Frozen universe snapshots are local, large and regenerable -- keep the dumps
# ignored but track the explanatory README.
data/snapshots/*.json
!data/snapshots/README.md
# Exception: the bridges endpoint is paywalled since 2026; this last public
# output (Wayback 2024-12-22) is NOT regenerable -- keep it tracked.
!data/snapshots/bridges_2026-07-11.json

